Given below is the cross pattern has the shape of the mathematical cross sign (X).

Input Format

Read no of rows

Constraints

1<=n<=10^7

Output Format

Cross pattern has the shape of the mathematical cross sign (X).

Sample Input 0

5
Sample Output 0

*   *
 * * 
  *  
 * * 
*   *
Sample Input 1

10
Sample Output 1

*        *
 *      * 
  *    *  
   *  *   
    **    
    **    
   *  *   
  *    *  
 *      * 
*        *
Sample Input 2

8
Sample Output 2

*      *
 *    * 
  *  *  
   **   
   **   
  *  *  
 *    * 
*      *



#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    int n;
    scanf("%d", &n);
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
            if (j == i || j == (n - 1 - i)) {
                printf("*");
            } else {
                printf(" ");
            }
        }
        printf("\n");
    }

    return 0;
}
